marriage equality referendum

00:06:12.180 --> 00:06:17.970
was an extremely limited view
of LGBT people and LGBT culture.

00:06:17.970 --> 00:06:22.290
So it was very much just
like, we're were two white,

00:06:22.290 --> 00:06:23.875
