wrong with any of those things.

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:33.900
Working at KPMG, that's fine.

00:06:33.900 --> 00:06:35.340
Having a pint is fine.

00:06:35.340 --> 00:06:36.810
Watching "The Late Late"--

00:06:36.810 --> 00:06:38.470
well, that's not so fine.

00:06:38.470 --> 00:06:42.210
But people have their own thing.

00:06:42.210 --> 00:06:48.030
