00:07:50.515 --> 00:07:51.890
Why do they have
to be like that?

00:07:51.890 --> 00:07:53.790
Why can't they just be normal?

00:07:53.790 --> 00:07:55.850
There's this whole idea
that the ultimate goal

00:07:55.850 --> 00:07:57.830
of the LGBT community
is to assimilate

00:07:57.830 --> 00:08:00.070
into a cis,
heteronormative mainstream.

00:08:00.070 --> 00:08:01.500
And that's just not the case.

00:08:01.500 --> 00:08:03.700
We just want to be tolerated,
want to be celebrated,

00:08:03.700 --> 00:08:05.730
and we want to be accepted.

00:08:05.730 --> 00:08:08.010
So there's a little
bit of complacency

00:08:08.010 --> 00:08:09.670
in post-marriage
referendum Ireland

00:08:09.670 --> 00:08:14.840
