part of systematic oppression.

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:30.380
You are, and I am, and we
all are in different ways,

00:10:30.380 --> 00:10:32.060
depending on our
privileges, depending

00:10:32.060 --> 00:10:33.920
on how we conduct ourselves.

00:10:33.920 --> 00:10:38.350
And that type of sentiment, "I
just treat people like people,"

00:10:38.350 --> 00:10:40.430
