said to shake off this idea

00:10:48.730 --> 00:10:51.250
that you have any
responsibility.

00:10:51.250 --> 00:10:55.060
So yeah-- not a big
fan of that sentiment.

00:10:55.060 --> 00:10:57.130
And labels being bad--

00:10:57.130 --> 00:10:58.150
