00:10:58.150 --> 00:11:00.340
Labels are bad.

00:11:00.340 --> 00:11:02.587
We're actually a big fan
of labels in the community.

00:11:02.587 --> 00:11:04.420
I don't know if you've
seen all the letters,

00:11:04.420 --> 00:11:07.240
but yeah, we like it.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:10.120
I think labels are bad if
labels have never served you.

00:11:10.120 --> 00:11:12.430
If you've never needed
to be defined by a label,

00:11:12.430 --> 00:11:16.190
if you are the majority
person in your community,

00:11:16.190 --> 00:11:17.950
then you've never
realized how labels

00:11:17.950 --> 00:11:20.500
can be good, because you've
only seen labels limiting you.

00:11:20.500 --> 00:11:22.650
You've only seen them
ever hindering you,

00:11:22.650 --> 00:11:25.582
who you are, in the sense that--

00:11:25.582 --> 00:11:27.290
men just used to be
men, and now, they're

00:11:27.290 --> 00:11:28.780
cis, straight, white men.

00:11:28.780 --> 00:11:31.570
And they don't like that at all.

00:11:31.570 --> 00:11:33.820
