when you're a minority,

00:11:33.820 --> 00:11:35.260
it helps you find
your community,

00:11:35.260 --> 00:11:37.810
helps you find people who've
had similar experiences to you.

00:11:37.810 --> 00:11:41.320
And that is really, really,
really a survival tactic.

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:44.000
So if we could do
away with labels,

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:46.570
then we'd do away
with our community.

00:11:46.570 --> 00:11:49.540
Is the ultimate goal maybe
to get rid of labels?

00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:50.800
Sure, OK, maybe.

00:11:50.800 --> 00:11:54.730
We're not there
