00:18:24.430 --> 00:18:27.100
and it's very difficult
and problematic

00:18:27.100 --> 00:18:28.480
for the rest of the community.

00:18:28.480 --> 00:18:31.540
I don't know if you noticed, but
G is actually just one letter.

00:18:31.540 --> 00:18:32.950
There's a bunch of others.

00:18:32.950 --> 00:18:35.530
And this brings us to a
problem with this acronym being

00:18:35.530 --> 00:18:37.840
actually a little limiting.

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:39.730
It doesn't really
serve us that well,

00:18:39.730 --> 00:18:43.210
because it's very front-loaded
with the most represented

00:18:43.210 --> 00:18:44.920
identities.

00:18:44.920 --> 00:18:47.980
And if people's
attention span is

00:18:47.980 --> 00:18:50.530
kind of front loaded as well,
and then you kind of trail off,

00:18:50.530 --> 00:18:53.980
then you're losing some of the
least represented identities

00:18:53.980 --> 00:18:56.650
as you go down the line.

00:18:56.650 --> 00:18:59.530
So it can be a limiting acronym.

00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:00.490
Great brand, though.

00:19:00.490 --> 00:19:03.031
Everyone recognizes it, so
you have to balance the two.

00:19:03.031 --> 00:19:03.530
OK.

00:19:03.530 --> 00:19:05.670
