00:20:23.399 --> 00:20:24.690
They might want to be romantic.

00:20:24.690 --> 00:20:26.460
They might have a
romantic attraction.

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:28.370
So you could be
asexual, but romantic.

00:20:28.370 --> 00:20:31.800
And within being asexual, you
could be asexual biromantic,

00:20:31.800 --> 00:20:33.900
panromantic, heteroromantic,
homoromantic--

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:35.970
so it's a whole thing.

00:20:35.970 --> 00:20:36.750
Yeah.

00:20:36.750 --> 00:20:39.180
Very under-represented,
