00:21:10.730 --> 00:21:11.550
Yeah.

00:21:11.550 --> 00:21:12.710
So P.

00:21:12.710 --> 00:21:13.850
AUDIENCE: Pansexual.

00:21:13.850 --> 00:21:16.475
BELLA FITZPATRICK: Pansexual, of
