00:43:53.710 --> 00:43:54.710
BELLA FITZPATRICK: Yeah.

00:43:54.710 --> 00:43:57.774
AUDIENCE: And how do
you respond to that?

00:43:57.774 --> 00:43:58.940
What's your tactic for that?

00:43:58.940 --> 00:44:01.315
BELLA FITZPATRICK: The classic
one we get on the internet

00:44:01.315 --> 00:44:04.249
is, I identify as an
attack helicopter.

00:44:04.249 --> 00:44:04.790
I don't know.

00:44:04.790 --> 00:44:06.590
All the anti-trans
people had a meeting

00:44:06.590 --> 00:44:08.390
