00:46:30.530 --> 00:46:33.290
Kill them with kindness, as
my granddad would always say.

00:46:33.290 --> 00:46:36.410
What can they come back as you
with if you say, oh, you're

00:46:36.410 --> 00:46:37.520
an attack helicopter?

00:46:37.520 --> 00:46:40.290
Right, so what pronouns
do you use, though?

00:46:40.290 --> 00:46:41.640
That's the answer.

