00:50:01.000 --> 00:50:03.980
They have all this rhetoric
around just being very, very

00:50:03.980 --> 00:50:04.480
polite.

00:50:04.480 --> 00:50:06.910
And ultimately, when you
are a marginalized group,

00:50:06.910 --> 00:50:09.160
you don't care about politeness.

00:50:09.160 --> 00:50:10.930
You don't care about Ps and Qs.

00:50:10.930 --> 00:50:12.782
You care about
systematic oppression,

00:50:12.782 --> 00:50:13.990
and they are holding that up.

00:50:13.990 --> 00:50:16.240
