00:52:53.170 --> 00:52:56.415
TENI just recently published
a report on gender norms

00:52:56.415 --> 00:52:57.790
in primary schools,
which is very

00:52:57.790 --> 00:53:02.500
troubling about how much we
force kids into gender norms.

00:53:02.500 --> 00:53:07.750
And this young child who might
be trans or might like dresses,

00:53:07.750 --> 00:53:08.440
you know?

00:53:08.440 --> 00:53:10.360
Those aren't necessarily
the same thing,

00:53:10.360 --> 00:53:12.610
and both should be accepted.

00:53:12.610 --> 00:53:16.570
Ultimately, parents have a
right to raise their kid however

00:53:16.570 --> 00:53:18.790
they want, but not
within child abuse.

00:53:18.790 --> 00:53:21.070
And forcing your child
to express themselves

00:53:21.070 --> 00:53:23.260
in a way that causes them
distress is child abuse.

00:53:23.260 --> 00:53:25.840
And we need to recognize
that and be more confident

00:53:25.840 --> 00:53:27.850
in our place in the right, OK?

00:53:27.850 --> 00:53:31.284
So we deal with schools
where parents have said,

00:53:31.284 --> 00:53:32.950
my kid's going through
a bit of a phase.

00:53:32.950 --> 00:53:34.150
They're using
they/them pronouns.

00:53:34.150 --> 00:53:36.108
I'd really appreciate it
if you didn't indulge.

00:53:36.108 --> 00:53:38.202
And we want teachers to
know they have the right

00:53:38.202 --> 00:53:40.660
to say, well, actually, whatever
you do in your own house--

00:53:40.660 --> 00:53:43.480
but in this school, we'll
respect the young person

00:53:43.480 --> 00:53:45.370
because young
people have rights.

00:53:45.370 --> 00:53:46.740
Young people have autonomy.

00:53:46.740 --> 00:53:49.430
And they are allowed to petition
the school board with regards

00:53:49.430 --> 00:53:49.930
to this.

00:53:49.930 --> 00:53:51.490
And they are allowed to go
to the children's ombudsman

00:53:51.490 --> 00:53:52.810
if they are unsatisfied.

00:53:52.810 --> 00:53:55.690
Because under the Equal
Status Act of 2015,

00:53:55.690 --> 00:53:59.620
continuous purposeful
use of incorrect pronouns

00:53:59.620 --> 00:54:01.880
can be considered harassment.

00:54:01.880 --> 00:54:05.260
So we shouldn't allow
what we consider

00:54:05.260 --> 00:54:08.350
to be personal preference
on how you raise

00:54:08.350 --> 00:54:09.760
your kids to allow child abuse.

00:54:09.760 --> 00:54:11.593
So that's what I would
say in that instance.

00:54:11.593 --> 00:54:13.110
I hope that kid is OK.

00:54:13.110 --> 00:54:13.850
Thanks.

